connection buildup!

1. install google-cloud-SDK
2. $gcloud init , login via OAuth2
3. Identity Access Management = IAM
    (read those later on if required)
4. adding team member for access
    menu -> IAM -> add+ -> select role and email and add
5. connect
    gcloud compute ssh seonils@instance-1


file transfer
@local terminal 
gcloud compute scp [from/filename] [to@instancename]


access (login)

gcloud compute ssh seonils@instance-3


